That is why

101
00:03:34,550 --> 00:03:35,950
we need an Acting Chairman now.

102
00:03:36,130 --> 00:03:38,380
So, let's vote.

103
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:41,210
If you agree on Mr. Ning's promotion,

104
00:03:41,890 --> 00:03:42,520
