125
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:53,460
Wanna mess with me? Your timing sucks.

126
00:04:54,310 --> 00:04:56,080
Or you'll be in trouble.

127
00:04:56,580 --> 00:04:59,770
Don't forget I've warned you.

128
00:05:07,130 --> 00:05:07,800
Hi, Miss Li.

129
