139
00:05:50,090 --> 00:05:50,830
Nope.

140
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,830
I just wanna look at you

141
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:55,660
from here.

142
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:58,510
I know you're worried about Mr. Li.

143
00:05:58,870 --> 00:06:00,220
But you should be calm and strong.

144
00:06:01,270 --> 00:06:02,480
You're really attractive

145
00:06:03,140 --> 00:06:04,510
and considerate.

146
00:06:06,940 --> 00:06:09,460
No wonder my dad was into you.

147
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:11,990
However,

148
00:06:12,050 --> 00:06:14,850
there's no way for you to marry my dad

149
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:18,600
and be a younger version of my mom.

150
00:06:19,290 --> 00:06:20,490
You're reading too much into it.

151
00:06:21,260 --> 00:06:23,000
