153
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:27,650
Watch your mouth!

154
00:06:35,420 --> 00:06:36,380
You're insane!

155
00:06:49,790 --> 00:06:52,860
Yang, I'm so sorry.

156
00:06:52,890 --> 00:06:53,980
I didn't mean to hurt you.

157
00:06:54,020 --> 00:06:56,050
Don't worry. It's fine.

158
00:06:57,950 --> 00:06:58,940
No big deal, OK?

159
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:00,930
