160
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,100
I'm sorry.

161
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,309
Did you forget to take the pills?

162
00:07:05,310 --> 00:07:05,600
Yes.

163
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,080
Remember it next time.

164
00:07:28,910 --> 00:07:30,200
I didn't know you're sick.

165
00:07:31,300 --> 00:07:32,290
So, I'll forgive you

166
00:07:32,940 --> 00:07:34,310
