167
00:07:36,950 --> 00:07:38,440
You witch! Stop there!

168
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,310
I'm gonna fire you!

169
00:07:39,490 --> 00:07:40,190
Stop!

170
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,880
